      "updated": 1775631021206,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Branden Eich 1995\nFirst Name - MOCHA -> Live Script -> JavaScript\n\nECMA(European Computer Manufacturing Association)\n1997 - ECMA Script (ES1)\n\nMost popular version - ES6\nLatest version - ES16\n\n\nFeatures\n\n-> JS is dynamically typed in nature\n-> It adds functionality\n-> Scripting language - does not need compilation, used to control other\napplication, runs line by line\n-> loosely type\n-> synchronous in nature by default\n\n\nvar - global scope, functional scope\nlet - local scope, script scope\nconst - local scope, script scope\n\nprimitive                           non primitive\n\nnumber                              array\nstring                              object\nboolean                             function\nnull\nundefined\nbigInt\nsymbol\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Branden Eich 1995\nFirst Name - MOCHA -> Live Script -> JavaScript\n\nECMA(European Computer Manufacturing Association)\n1997 - ECMA Script (ES1)\n\nMost popular version - ES6\nLatest version - ES16\n\n\nFeatures\n\n-> JS is dynamically typed in nature\n-> It adds functionality\n-> Scripting language - does not need compilation, used to control other\napplication, runs line by line\n-> loosely type\n-> synchronous in nature by default\n\n\nvar - global scope, functional scope\nlet - local scope, script scope\nconst - local scope, script scope\n\nprimitive                           non primitive\n\nnumber                              array\nstring                              object\nboolean                             function\nnull\nundefined\nbigInt\nsymbol\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
